projects.name: Home Rental Booking System
projects.description: Developed a rental booking system with a responsive, user-friendly interface. Implemented secure user login and registration with session management. Utilized EJS for dynamic content rendering based on user inputs. Built backend services to handle listings, bookings, user accounts, and reviews. Enabled CRUD operations for rental properties with dynamic pricing logic.

projects.name: Diary Website
projects.description: Developed a web-based diary application for users to create, edit, and delete diary entries. Implemented secure user authentication and session management. Utilized JSP for dynamic web content and Servlets for handling user requests. Integrated JDBC for database connectivity and CRUD operations. Designed an intuitive user interface for enhanced user experience.

projects.name: Quiz Web Application
projects.description: Developed a quiz web application using React that dynamically renders questions and tracks user progress. Utilized React state management to handle user interactions and display real-time results. Implemented a scoring system to enhance user engagement. Designed a responsive UI using HTML, CSS, and React components.

experiences.description: Created a Job Portal with Bootstrap and Django. Developed a responsive interface for job listings and applications. Implemented secure login and data management using Djangos authentication system. Configured Django forms for seamless user data handling and validation.
